fn.p:
Principles for Responsible Investment (2011) participants agree to:


incorporate ESG [environmental, social, and governance] issues into investment analysis and decision making processes;

be active owners and incorporate ESG issues into ownership policies and practices;

seek appropriate disclosure on ESG issues by the entities in which we invest;

promote acceptance and implementation of the Principles within the investment industry;

work together to enhance effectiveness in implementing the Principles; and

each report on our activities and progress toward implementing the Principles.
